tossup_question: 17) PHYSICS  Edward weighs 65 kilograms, and Jinwoo weighs a whopping 120 kilograms due to his recent excessive love of food. If Edward collides into Jinwoo, which of the following is true?
tossup_MCQoptions:
W) Edward experiences a greater force than Jinwoo
X) Jinwoo experiences a greater force than Edward
Y) Both Jinwoo and Edward experience the same force
Z) There is not enough information to determine who experiences more force.
tossup_answer: ANSWER: Y) Both Jinwoo and Edward experience the same force
